=== Members ===

 Current members
* Fred Schendel – keyboards, guitars, lead and backing vocals , drums 
* Steve Babb – bass, keyboards, lead and backing backing vocals , percussion 
* Aaron Raulston - drums 
* Hannah Pryor – lead vocals 

Former members
* Michelle Young – lead vocals , keyboards 
* Walter Moore – drums , lead vocals, guitar 
* Susie Bogdanowicz - lead vocals 
* Carl Groves – lead vocals 
* Jon Davison – lead vocals 
* Kamran Alan Shikoh – guitars, electric sitar 
Former session/guest musicians
* David Carter – guitars 
* Brad Marler – lead vocals 
* Terry Clouse – guitars 
* Sarah Snyder – vocals 
* Bethany Warren (Susie Bogdanowicz&#x27;s younger sister) – vocals 
* Flo Paris – vocals 
* Matt Mendians – drums 
* The Adonia String Trio – string trio 
** Rebecca James – violin
** Susan Whitacre – viola
** Rachel Beckmann/Hackenberger – cello
* David Wallimann – guitars 
* Randall Williams – drums 
