When the graph &quot;G&quot; is &quot;d&quot;-regular, there is a relationship between &quot;h&quot;(&quot;G&quot;) and the spectral gap &quot;d&quot; − λ2 of &quot;G&quot;. An inequality due to Dodziuk and independently Alon and Milman states that

